  "title": "Physiotherapy Aide | Geriatric Rehab",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Assist resident through prescribed therapeutic exercises and activities to enhance overall physical function</li>\n  <li>Assist PT and OT with the activities for resident </li>\n  <li>Monitor treatment compliance and record developmental milestones or concerns</li>\n  <li>Setup equipment for therapy session and ensure area is clean and safe</li>\n  <li>Observe and report resident progress or challenges to the occupational therapist</li>\n  <li>Support the occupational therapist during group therapy session</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Requirements:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>WSQ Certificate in Healthcare Support (Therapy Support), or NITEC in Community Care &amp; Social Services</li>\n  <li>Min 2 years experience in healthcare or therapy</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Check out http://abercare.sg/jobs-vacancies/ for more details</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested applicants may email your updated resume to career@abercare.sg</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Abercare.sg | EA License No. 18C9070 | KOH SU WEN, CLARISSA| Registration No. R24119504|</p>",
